# Design Systems Convention

## Struktura preset

⚠ **Upstream convention** (confirmed Phase 3): primary file is `tokens.css` (CSS variables w `:root`) NIE `tokens.example.json`. Per `design-systems/_schema/AGENTS.md` + upstream lint w `apps/daemon/src/lint-artifact.ts`. Roduq presets provide both.

```
design-systems/roduq-<preset-name>/         # ← prefix 'roduq-' żeby coexist z upstream 152 design systems
├── DESIGN.md                      # Main spec (palette + typography + voice + layout)
├── tokens.css                     # PRIMARY — upstream contract + Roduq extensions
├── tokens.example.json            # SECONDARY — JSON Schema v1 preview dla Phase 5 ajv
├── inspiration.md                 # Industry references + URL screenshots
└── samples/
    └── full-page.html             # Renderable demo (primary canonical artifact)
    # Optional dla canonical preset (default): hero.html / features.html / cta.html / pricing.html
```

Naming: ZAWSZE `roduq-<preset>` prefix. Upstream already has `default/`, `warm-editorial/` — naming collision avoided via prefix.

