## tokens.css structure — dual-layer (Roduq pattern)

Upstream lint contract z `craft/color.md` (lint-enforced):
- Neutrals: `--bg`, `--surface`, `--fg`, `--muted`, `--border`
- Accent: `--accent` (SINGLE — max 2 visible uses per screen)
- Accent states: `--accent-hover`, `--accent-active`, `--accent-on`
- Semantic: `--success`, `--warn`, `--danger`
- Typography: `--font-display`, `--font-body`, `--font-mono`

Schema extensions (optional, alias to richer siblings via `var()`): `--fg-2`, `--meta`, `--surface-warm`, `--border-soft`.

Roduq dual-layer pattern:
```css
:root {
  /* Layer 1: Upstream contract (lint-enforced) */
  --bg: #FAFAFA; --surface: #FFFFFF; --fg: #0F0F0F;
  --muted: #525252; --meta: #737373;
  --border: #E5E5E5; --border-soft: rgba(15,15,15,0.06);
  --accent: #2563EB; --accent-on: #FFFFFF;
  --accent-hover: color-mix(in oklab, var(--accent), black 8%);
  --success: #10B981; --warn: #F59E0B; --danger: #EF4444;
  --font-display: "Inter Tight", ...; --font-body: "Inter", ...; --font-mono: ...;

  /* Layer 2: Roduq extensions (used by skills templates from Phase 2) */
  --color-brand-primary: var(--accent);
  --color-surface-default: var(--surface);
  --space-md: 1rem; --text-base: 1rem; --radius-md: 0.5rem;
  /* ... full scale tokens — see roduq-default/tokens.css canonical */
}
```

Dark mode: `--accent-hover` z `white` mix (NIE black) — light accents na dark bg already low-contrast.

